data.description: Welcome, this beautifully updated 3-bedroom 2-bath single family home is located just a few miles from Tyndall Air Force Base, shopping, schools, and hospitals.  The back patio is large enough for grilling, entertaining, and has great yard space with plenty of room for kids to play or pets to run. An updated kitchen with new stainless-steel appliances, custom soft close cabinetry, and butcher block countertops are joined to the living and dining room. Measurements are approximate verify if important.
